One time install for live stats

1) Put the files in your web directory
2) Navigate to the web directory on the web server and run this command:

composer install --ignore-platform-reqs
composer require gmostafa/php-graphql-client


3) edit your settings.php to look how you would like

4) setup cron job to do the following

change the 5 to however often you want to update the stats (note: change the setting refreshJSONCache in settings.php to coincide)

crontab -e

*/2 * * * * wget --spider --timeout=0 --tries=1 "https://riskmoon.com/token/?action=update"